Name: STATIC: Investigator Training
About the game: In Static: Investigator Training, you will play the role of Julie Masters, an ambitious fan of all things Paranormal; who recently requested membership with Berkshire Paranormal. Julie will investigate the mansion and surrounding areas collecting evidence; though paranormal events have been documented at the mansion Julie ends up uncovering an interesting addition to the ghostly history.
